sql:
SELECT AVG(rating) AS average_rating
FROM song_ratings
WHERE song_id = '0';

external_knowledge:
Highly praised songs refer to songs with an average rating greater than 3 out of 5; 
A particular music lover refers to the user with an ID of 1; 
Struck a chord with them refers to the play count of the song.

